  <parts>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Paullus</portrait>
      <speaker_name>Paullus</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“What brings you here?” inquires Paullus.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>dlgCam(15, 40, 6, 8005);</string>
        <string>DOOR_PaulusOffice.close();</string>
        <string>dlgTeleportToMarker(TM_DLG_Paullus_PC);</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I have a proposition for you, Dux.” Tell him about the temple.</text>
          <def_link>9315</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9314</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Paullus</portrait>
      <speaker_name>Paullus</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“Quite a mess,” states Paullus, his eyes distant. “Can it be killed?” He asks the question as if going through a list of options, starting with the simplest solution.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Maybe. Maybe not. It took the Empire everything they had to bring down four of these things.”</text>
          <def_link>9316</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9315</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Paullus</portrait>
      <speaker_name>Paullus</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“Alright,” says Paullus. He doesn’t sound convinced but he doesn’t argue either. “Can we work with him?”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I don’t see why not. Agathoth needs a man like you and a man like you can use the power Agathoth brings to the table. It’s win-win, Dux.”</text>
          <def_link>9317</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9316</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Paullus</portrait>
      <speaker_name>Paullus</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“As I understand, he wants a puppet not a partner.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What one wants and what one gets are often two different things.”</text>
          <def_link>9318</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Which is why I came to you, Dux. You’re strong enough to do things your way.”</text>
          <def_link>9318</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“He can’t make every decision and solve every problem himself. He will set the course and you’ll steer the ship.”</text>
          <def_link>9318</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9317</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Paullus</portrait>
      <speaker_name>Paullus</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“I must admit, it’s not an alliance I had in mind.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Why be second to some lord when you can be second to a god and rule all in his name?”</text>
          <def_link>9321</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“You could have made an alliance with any House a long time ago but you waited for a better offer. The wait is over, Dux. This is the best offer you’re ever going to get.”</text>
          <def_link>9321</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear>aod.ending_gnz_IG_joins_HA == false || aod.ending_gnz_IG_joins_HC == false</checkOnAppear>
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“One way or another, Agathoth will rule this world. You can embrace the change or be consumed by it. These are your only options, Dux.”</text>
          <def_link>9321</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9318</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Paullus</portrait>
      <speaker_name>Paullus</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“Very well,” nods Paullus. “Take me to him.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Without an escort?”</text>
          <def_link>9322</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9321</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“An escort will attract too much attention,” says Paullus, shaking his head. “Don’t worry, I still remember how to hold a sword.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What about Carbo?”</text>
          <def_link>9323</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9322</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Carbo is a simple man who believes in simple things. It would be unwise to burden him with what you’ve just told me. Besides, should anything happen to me, he’ll take over and... do what needs to be done.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I’ll need supplies. Did my things arrive yet?”</text>
          <def_link>9324</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9323</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Your chest? It arrived before you did. Tell the guards outside to bring it here if they didn't already.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>aod.end_xp_paullus = 1;</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>Leave.</text>
          <def_link>9328</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9324</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>END - stash</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>VCO_Stash.setActive(1);</string>
        <string>setObjectRenderState(obj_stash, 1);</string>
        <string>aod.end_xp_paullus = 1;</string>
        <string>dlgFinish();</string>
        <string>dlgFadeShortToThisPart();</string>
        <string>dlgCam(45, 45, 15);</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers />
      <UID>9328</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>END</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>dlgFinish();</string>
        <string>dlgFadeShortToThisPart();</string>
        <string>dlgCam(45, 45, 15);</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers />
